We felt safe and secure with our small children.	Hassle to get from ship to hotel, hassle to get correct rate, hassle with hotel safe (should have one in room anyway), and a hassle to get to the airport the next morning.	I was there by myself and felt very safe.	This hotel is by a small lake and at dusk there are misquitos and misc.	Decided to stay one night by the airport and used priceline to get a room and ended up with the doubletree at a good rate!	Free shuttle to and from airport helps.	This hotel is clean, neat and offers good value for the money.